### Workbench health — expect CSV-seeded local data
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/CustomerNotes?$top=2

### LogisticsService (bundled CAP provider, port 4455) direct ping
GET http://localhost:4455/odata/v4/logistics/Carriers

### FXService (bundled REST provider, port 4456) direct ping
GET http://localhost:4456/

### Northwind V4 public service — reached through the workbench as `Customers`
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Customers?$top=1

### Northwind V2 public service — reached through the workbench as `Products`
GET http://localhost:4005/odata/v4/sales-intel/Products?$top=1
